How to do Database connection 
=> there are mainly two ways to connect database 

1.  database se jab bhi hum baat karne ki kosis karenge toh problem aa sakti hai 
    i.e we need to wrap things up in Try/Catch or Promises

2.  and database is present in another continent i.e database se jab bhi baat karenge toh time lagta hai 
    so Async/Await lagana hi padega 